```

### Monorepo Structure

```
perfect-world/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/                    # Public website + Player Dashboard (Next.js 16)
│   ├── api/                    # Backend microservices (NestJS)
│   ├── admin/                  # Admin Panel (Next.js 16)
│   └── launcher/               # Desktop launcher (Electron/Tauri)
├── packages/
│   ├── ui/                     # Shared UI components (Neo Brutalism design system)
│   ├── auth/                   # Authentication utilities (JWT, OAuth helpers)
│   ├── configs/                # Shared configurations (ESLint, TypeScript, Tailwind)
│   ├── sdk/                    # API client SDK (typed fetch wrappers)
│   ├── database/               # Prisma schema, migrations, seed scripts
│   └── shared/                 # Common types, constants, validation schemas
├── docker-compose.yml          # Local dev environment (PG, Redis)
├── turbo.json                  # Turborepo pipeline configuration
├── package.json                # Root workspace configuration
└── .github/workflows/          # CI/CD pipelines
```

### Request Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Browser)
    participant N as Next.js (SSR/RSC)
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant S as Service
    participant D as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant WS as Socket.IO

    C->>N: Page Request
    N->>G: Server-side data fetch
    G->>G: Rate limit check
    G->>G: JWT validation
    G->>S: Route to service
    S->>R: Check cache
    alt Cache hit
        R-->>S: Cached data
    else Cache miss
        S->>D: Query database
        D-->>S: Result
        S->>R: Update cache
    end
    S-->>G: Response
    G-->>N: JSON data
    N-->>C: Rendered HTML + hydration

    Note over C,WS: Realtime updates
    C->>WS: Connect (JWT auth)
    WS->>R: Subscribe to channels
    R-->>WS: Pub/Sub event
    WS-->>C: Push update
```

